  %section(data-state="" )
    .title-information
    %h2 Tips & Tricks - ssh scavenger hunt
    :markdown
      * Choose an app that you've created. What public IP address is using? (hint: host or dig)
      * Use web console or CLI tools, find ssh login for an app. (hint: rhc domain show)
      * Now, ssh into the application. What is your home directory? (hint: pwd)
      * Try to list all home directories. (hint: ls)
      * What private IP addresses is your app using? (hint: env)
      * `How much memory is this app using? (hint: oo-cgroup-read memory.usage_in_bytes)i`
      * `Stop your app and check the memory usage (hint: ctl_app graceful-stop)`
      * `Restart your app (hint: ctl_app start)`

